{"tid":2422923,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"名潮食館感染群組擴大　梁子超料有超級傳播者   衛生署：消毒後無須停業","createTime":"2021-02-25T14:17:50.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-26T12:52:52.000Z","uid":79563,"like":9,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":27,"replies":[{"pid":"b8700e90b15f7f15cc2ad0adfe134e2d62b38183","tid":2422923,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:17:50.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577547-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577547-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=b936743d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577547-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=e7d9a0f5\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577547-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀K11 Musea食肆「名潮食館」的新型肺炎感染群組擴大，確診個案由1宗急升至6宗，另有5宗初步確診，累計個案增至11宗，3宗是食肆員工，8宗食客的個案，都是在2月18和19日曾在餐廳午饍。<br />\n<br />\n呼吸系統專科醫生梁子超表示，估計食肆有高病毒排放量的超級傳播者出現，令病毒經由長距離或空氣傳播，導致多人感染，不排除會有更多人感染。他估計，經員工傳播的機會較大，但即使源頭是餐廳員工，亦未必一定是現時確診的3名員工，因為最早發病和傳播的源頭，可能已痊癒，需要了解員工是否有抗體。<br />\n<br />\n他認為，感染風險不限於2月18和19日中午到過食店的顧客，如果病毒經由帶病毒的員工傳播，在18日或以後光顧過的食客，都有風險，建議近期到過「名潮食館」的市民，都要做檢測。<br />\n<br />\n梁子超認為，今次是個別現象，但亦反映社區仍有好多傳播源頭，在疫情仍未完全控制前，放寬社交距離措施，便有機會出現類似的傳播。他認為，食肆員工14日一檢，相距的時間太長，建議負責人發現員工有病徵或其家人有感染風險，便要安排員工盡早檢測。"},{"pid":"f3973abec47e50165b52f6b94f199c51e7ef4dd0","tid":2422923,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:18:31.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577551-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577551-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFUB1UtkZy1G9%2FYekDAkGV2Y%3D&h=9c26e730\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1577551-20210225.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=be7e0e13\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1577551-20210225.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n本港新增13宗新型肺炎確診，3宗是源頭不明本地個案。<br />\n<br />\n尖沙咀的「名潮食館」感染群組擴大，累計出現6宗確診和5宗初步確診，當中包括3名食肆員工和8名食客。衞生防護中心估計，餐廳內可能出現傳播。"},{"pid":"821c46f4c97f06800b914e00ceb7f69fb4b2bec8","tid":2422923,"uid":156652,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"咁停乜七酒吧？"},{"pid":"3ba77452c39da05c04e442fd6ce4b4fe008d896a","tid":2422923,"uid":79563,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:19:20.000Z","msg":"張竹君係咪話, 食客唔係密切接觸者?<br />\n<br />\n其實一直以嚟, 根本都都係任佢UP, 毫無準則"},{"pid":"f32a470d7ff80960a8e096e53a8c673d3a85c172","tid":2422923,"uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"821c46f4c97f06800b914e00ceb7f69fb4b2bec8","tid":2422923,"uid":156652,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T14:19:19.000Z","msg":"咁停乜七酒吧？"},"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:13:28.000Z","msg":"酒吧飲野會kiss <br />\n你去過酒吧未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9befaffbb5acc08c947527a327f639abc185f052","tid":2422923,"uid":174013,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:19:39.000Z","msg":"間鋪有乜野後台? 咁都唔洗封鋪送班員工入營?"},{"pid":"1e84d1693675c8193d0b9cff3d3345aa64ca714e","tid":2422923,"uid":48234,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T15:21:57.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"gold\">諗都唔駛諗就知道係藍店<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"e48c8150c6a65a9623f6fa14c9693eb7153cef11","tid":2422923,"uid":156652,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"f32a470d7ff80960a8e096e53a8c673d3a85c172","tid":2422923,"uid":122377,"like":1,"dislike":19,"score":-18,"quote":{"pid":"821c46f4c97f06800b914e00ceb7f69fb4b2bec8","tid":2422923,"uid":156652,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedB